high_descs: Turn left and walk to the window and then turn left and walk to the middle of the stove and the counter.
Pick up the spatula.
Take a step left.
Put the spatula in the pan on the back left burner.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it.
Turn left and walk to the door then turn right.
Put the pan on the right edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Move to stand where the stove meets the last piece of counter space against the wall.
Pick up the spatula from the counter.
Carry the spatula to stand at the other side of the stove.
Place the spatula in the bowl on the back left side of the stove.
Pick up the bowl with the spatula in it.
Carry the bowl and spatula to the white table in the corner of the room.
Place the bowl with the spatula in it on the right end of the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl with a spatula in it to the white table.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the end, turn left
grab the spatula on the counter
walk to the left a little
put the spatula in the pan on the rear left stove
take the pan with the spatula in it
turn left, walk to the white table by the door
put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: put the spatula in the pan on the rear left stove, move the pan to the table

high_descs: Turn left, then go straight, then turn left to face the stove.
Pick up the spatula on the counter, to the right of the stove.
Turn left, then turn right to face the stove.
Put the spatula in the pot, in the back left corner of the stove.
Pick up the pot with the spatula in it, from the stove.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right to face the table near the door.
Place the pot on the right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with a spatula in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the window, turn left, face the stove.
Pick up the spatula on the counter.
Bring the spatula to the left and face the stove. of the stove.
Put the spatula in the left pot on the stove.
Pick up the pot with spatula on the left of the stove.
Turn left, head to the door, turn right and face the white table.
Put the pot with spatula on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pot with spatula on the table.
